Gomekpɔkpɔ na sitsoƒe kude amesiwo kpefu le duta ʋliʋli ƒe wɔna wo me nye gomekpɔkpɔ tɔxɛ ade si dzi kpedodo le le Germany ƒe dukplɔ se  me. Enya sia ŋti bubu fia be dukplɔ gbalěa de dzesi gɔmesese si ke 1951 Refugee Convention na kuɖe sitsoƒe ŋu be edua manyǎ sitsoƒedzilawo o ke boŋ woa kpɔ wo ta le esea te. Takpɔkpɔ sia le veviě na Federal Office For Migration and Refugees  (Bundesamt für Migration und Flüchtlinge, 'BAMF') fukpekpe adeke manɔ mee.<ref>[http://www.asylumineurope.org/reports/country/germany An overview of the history of asylum in Germany]</ref>

